{"title":"MySql 索引(index)","date":"2020-04-07T15:02:42.224Z","link":"post/370","categories":["MySql"],"updated":"2020-04-09T15:04:39.203Z","content":"<p>date: 2020-04-07 22:42:22</p>\n<h2 id=\"tags-MySql\">tags: MySql<a href=\"post/370#tags-MySql\"></a></h2><h2 id=\"1-索引的概念\">1.索引的概念<a href=\"post/370#1-索引的概念\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">是帮助MySql高效获取数据的数据结构。排好序的快速查找数据结构</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2-索引数据结构\">2.索引数据结构<a href=\"post/370#2-索引数据结构\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1、BTree 索引（主要）</span><br><span class=\"line\">2、Hash索引</span><br><span class=\"line\">3、full-text全文索引</span><br><span class=\"line\">4、R-Tree索引</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-BTree数据结构图示\">2.1 BTree数据结构图示<a href=\"post/370#2-1-BTree数据结构图示\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-bde60c8f3451da0e630630281498a1e0_720w.png\" alt=\"avatar\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-适合创建索引条件\">3.适合创建索引条件<a href=\"post/370#3-适合创建索引条件\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1、主键自动建立唯一索引</span><br><span class=\"line\">2、频繁作为查询条件的字段应该建立索引</span><br><span class=\"line\">3、查询中与其他表关联的字段，外键关系建立索引</span><br><span class=\"line\">4、单键/组合索引的选择问题，组合索引性价比更高</span><br><span class=\"line\">5、查询中排序的字段，排序字段若通过索引去访问将大大提高排序效率</span><br><span class=\"line\">6、查询中统计或者分组字段</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"4-不适合创建索引条件\">4.不适合创建索引条件<a href=\"post/370#4-不适合创建索引条件\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1、表记录少的</span><br><span class=\"line\">2、经常增删改的表或者字段</span><br><span class=\"line\">3、where条件里用不到的字段不创建索引</span><br><span class=\"line\">4、过滤性不好的不适合建索引</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","prev":{"title":"MySql explain","link":"post/371"},"next":{"title":"MySql常用函数","link":"post/369"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/370/","toc":[{"title":"1.索引的概念","id":"1-索引的概念","index":"1"},{"title":"2.索引数据结构","id":"2-索引数据结构","index":"2","children":[{"title":"2.1 BTree数据结构图示","id":"2-1-BTree数据结构图示","index":"2.1"}]},{"title":"3.适合创建索引条件","id":"3-适合创建索引条件","index":"3"},{"title":"4.不适合创建索引条件","id":"4-不适合创建索引条件","index":"4"}]}